snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedExtends

client = AsyncSeedExtends(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.extended_inline_request_body(
        unique="unique",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
